description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Chelsea and Westminster NHS Trust are recruiting bank Staff Nurses on both the Chelsea and West Middlesex sites. We have positions available for registered Staff Nurses who enjoy the variety of working in different clinical areas and who enjoy work that suits your lifestyle and fits in with your commitments. Staff Nurses who wish to work early shifts, late shifts and long days would be of particular interest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For these vacancies we require applications from individuals who have at least 6 months experience in care through the NHS. Please note that If you do not meet this requirement your application will not be considered.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Whilst covering a shift, you will be responsible for the implementation of evidence-based nursing care, working collaboratively and co-operatively with others to meet the needs of patients and their families.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As well as competitive pay rates, you’ll be eligible for many benefits of working as a permanent member of staff , including:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;• The chance to gain experience within a variety of departments&lt;br /&gt;• NHS Pension Scheme &lt;br /&gt;• NHS badge entitling you to discounts &lt;br /&gt;• Unsocial hours enhancements (where applicable)&lt;br /&gt;• Weekly pay&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are a committed, motivated reliable trained nurse who would enjoy the flexibility that ad hoc work brings, as well as the opportunity to experience different clinical settings working in this busy, diverse hospital this may be the job for you!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
